<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to Eventku - Organizer</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7f6;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .feature-item {
      flex: 1 1 45%;
      background: #f8fbff;
      border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .feature-item strong {
      display: block;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #0056b3;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f1f3f5;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6c757d;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Eventku!</h1>
      <p>Your journey as a top-tier Organizer starts here.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>Congratulations! Your Organizer account has been successfully created. We are excited to support you in creating memorable experiences.</p>

      <p>Your specialized toolkit is ready. Here is what you can do:</p>

