        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <strong>ðŸŽ« Custom Tickets</strong>
          Create various ticket types and vouchers.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="btn">Start Creating Events</a>
      </div>

      <p>Need help getting started? Reply to this email or visit our Help Center.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The Eventku Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Eventku. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
